The '''Buccaneer''', also known as the '''KYZOKU''' or '''Privateer''', is an enemy in ''[[Final Fantasy]]''. It can be encountered at [[Sea (location)#Final Fantasy|sea]]. It is not a threat to the [[party]], and can be easily defeated with a barrage of physical blows. It is a good source of [[gil]] for an early enemy.

